<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.9">
<l>keṇṭai yoṇkaṇun tuyilu meṉniṟam</l>
<l>paṇṭu paṇṭupō lokkum mikkacīrt</l>
<l>toṇṭa riṭṭapūn tuḷaviṉ vācamē</l>
<l>vaṇṭu koṇṭuvan tūtu mākilē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My keṇṭai fish[-shaped] bright eyes will sleep</l>
<l>And my coloring will be like before, [only] if</l>
<l>The [wings of] bees waft and bring the fragrance</l>
<l>Of the fresh tulasī offered by many fine devotees.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
